gov.ca.dmv.ease.ecs.request.factory
Interface IEcsRequestFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
EcsRequestFactory
public interface IEcsRequestFactory

Description: Interface for an object producing service requests. This factory is to be called by ECS clients. The requests produced by the factory follow the Command Pattern and they can be executed directly. More creation methods will be added over time. File: IExternalServiceRequestFactory.java Module: gov.ca.dmv.ease.ecs Created: Mar 17, 2009
